choices.text: the arrival of Benedict XVI to the office of the Pope. He is also a first Slav pope in the history of the Church. His arrival to the helm of the Church created a lot of noise all over the world. Some expressed their surprise, some tried to voice their concern. I must say that the Polish Church was also overwhelmed with the event. However, as far as the Polish Episcopate is concerned, Providence was guiding the Church's leaders, allowing them to discern promptly the signals which BAS sent to the Church to support the Polish stance in the pontificate transition.Although Benedict XVI was introduced by some as an ultra-opponent of the liberation theology, he in practice proved to be a real defense of the poor and a firm supporter of Mother Church. On the other side, Mr. Wojtyla was loved by all the people, both in the East and West, by those who fight in the most dangerous trenches and by the intellectuals and provocateurs.After the vacancy of the papacy, it is very good to remind the Pope that he is the head of an organization of nearly one billion people in the world. Everyone can view the arrival of a new occupant of a throne, a change of the chief of a big company, agriculture cooperative and so on.
